#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.79"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.79:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.79:0.2"
msgid "8. Ākaṅkhavagga"
msgstr "8. If You Want"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.79:0.3"
msgid "79. Āghātavatthusutta"
msgstr "79. Grounds for Resentment"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.79:1.1"
msgid "“Dasayimāni, bhikkhave, āghātavatthūni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are ten grounds for resentment."

msgctxt "an10.79:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni dasa?"
msgstr "What ten?"

msgctxt "an10.79:1.3"
msgid "‘Anatthaṃ me acarī’ti āghātaṃ bandhati;"
msgstr "Thinking: ‘They did wrong by me,’ you harbor resentment."

msgctxt "an10.79:1.4"
msgid "‘anatthaṃ me caratī’ti āghātaṃ bandhati;"
msgstr "Thinking: ‘They are doing wrong by me’ …"

msgctxt "an10.79:1.5"
msgid "‘anatthaṃ me carissatī’ti āghātaṃ bandhati;"
msgstr "‘They will do wrong by me’ …"

msgctxt "an10.79:1.6"
msgid "‘piyassa me manāpassa anatthaṃ acarī’ti … pe …"
msgstr "‘They did wrong by someone I love’ …"

msgctxt "an10.79:1.7"
msgid "‘anatthaṃ caratī’ti … pe …"
msgstr "‘They are doing wrong by someone I love’ …"

msgctxt "an10.79:1.8"
msgid "‘anatthaṃ carissatī’ti āghātaṃ bandhati, "
msgstr "‘They will do wrong by someone I love’ … "

msgctxt "an10.79:1.9"
msgid "‘appiyassa me amanāpassa atthaṃ acarī’ti … pe …"
msgstr "‘They helped someone I dislike’ …"

msgctxt "an10.79:1.10"
msgid "‘atthaṃ caratī’ti … pe …"
msgstr "‘They are helping someone I dislike’ …"

msgctxt "an10.79:1.11"
msgid "‘atthaṃ carissatī’ti āghātaṃ bandhati;"
msgstr "Thinking: ‘They will help someone I dislike,’ you harbor resentment."

msgctxt "an10.79:1.12"
msgid "aṭṭhāne ca kuppati—"
msgstr "You get angry for no reason."

msgctxt "an10.79:1.13"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, dasa āghātavatthūnī”ti."
msgstr "These are the ten grounds for resentment.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.79:1.14"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
